sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Administrator
    participant UI as Frontend UI
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Audit as Audit Log
    
    Admin->>UI: Buka menu Users
    UI->>API: Request daftar user
    API->>DB: Ambil data user
    DB-->>API: Return user list
    API-->>UI: Return users data
    UI->>Admin: Tampilkan daftar user
    
    alt Add User
        Admin->>UI: Klik Add User
        UI->>Admin: Tampilkan form input user
        Admin->>UI: Isi form user
        UI->>API: Kirim data user baru
        API->>Auth: Hash password
        Auth-->>API: Return password hash
        API->>DB: Simpan user baru
        DB-->>API: User tersimpan
        API->>Audit: Log user_create
        Audit->>DB: Simpan log audit
        API-->>UI: Return sukses
        UI->>Admin: Tampilkan user berhasil ditambahkan
        
    else Edit User
        Admin->>UI: Klik Edit User
        UI->>Admin: Tampilkan form edit
        Admin->>UI: Update data user
        UI->>API: Kirim perubahan data
        API->>DB: Update user
        DB-->>API: User terupdate
        API->>Audit: Log user_update
        Audit->>DB: Simpan log audit
        API-->>UI: Return sukses
        UI->>Admin: Tampilkan perubahan tersimpan
        
    else Delete User
        Admin->>UI: Klik Delete User
        UI->>API: Request hapus user
        API->>DB: Hapus user
        DB-->>API: User dihapus
        API->>Audit: Log user_delete
        Audit->>DB: Simpan log audit
        API-->>UI: Return sukses
        UI->>Admin: Tampilkan user berhasil dihapus
        
    else Reset Password
        Admin->>UI: Klik Reset Password
        UI->>Admin: Tampilkan dialog reset password
        Admin->>UI: Input password baru
        UI->>API: Kirim password baru
        API->>Auth: Hash password baru
        Auth-->>API: Return password hash
        API->>DB: Update password user
        DB-->>API: Password terupdate
        API->>Audit: Log password_reset
        Audit->>DB: Simpan log audit
        API-->>UI: Return sukses
        UI->>Admin: Tampilkan password berhasil direset
    end
